==German==
===Etymology===
From the Indo-European root ''*wer-u'' "to protect".
===Verb===
'''wehren'''
# do [[defend]]
#: ''Ich wollte mich doch nur '''wehren'''!'' - I only tried to defend myself
#: '''''Wehret''' den Anfängen!'' 

